						offset).round(0.001));
					});
				);
		slide = GUI.slider.new(procWindow, Rect(0, 0, thisWidth * 0.55, thisHeight))
			.value_(spec.unmap(proc.amp.ampdb).round(0.01))
			.action_({arg me; 
				var newamp;
